{"tid":2506421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"精液含「神秘物質」可預防癡呆！科學家讓果蠅吃精，發現牠的腦力明顯提升","createTime":"2021-04-27T09:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T10:42:17.000Z","uid":391580,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"78a8372d9a3e5db47b53d526061185e97b49f06d","tid":2506421,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T09:57:13.000Z","msg":"精液雖是體內代謝物，但近日一項最新研究發現，精液內含一種神秘物質，竟具有改善大腦衰退的功能！<br />\n<br />\n這項研究於本月13日發表於細胞生物學期刊《Cell Reports》上，是由德國柏林自由大學所提出的研究，研究員以成年果蠅為實驗對象，在果蠅大腦中，真核生物翻譯起始因子eIF5A的羥丁賴氨酸修飾（hypusination）水平原先會隨著年齡漸增而持續下降。<br />\n<br />\n但當研究員設法讓成年果蠅食用精液中含有的物質「亞精胺」後，發現果蠅腦內的線粒體障礙情形改善了，大腦的衰老狀況也獲得減緩。<br />\n<br />\n不僅具抗衰老功能，亞精胺也具心血管保護功能，且能增強免疫力，甚至對於抗癌也有部分功效。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSUtdgNFg8QbWk6MwunksGmoJ8RsymD3fWb4KqeBHtYWo?filename=Xq29g8m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXq29g8m.jpg&h=6087d1d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而其實對於精液的研究，最早可以回溯至1674年，名為Antonie Philips van Leeuwenhoek的科學家就以光學顯微鏡發現精液中含有特殊晶體，直至250年後，這項晶體才被發現含有腐胺、精胺、亞精胺。而亞精胺便是被發現具有抗衰老的關鍵之一。<br />\n<br />\n然而除了精液以外，科學家也表示，在豆類、奶油和蘑菇中的真核細胞中，也含有亞精胺。"},{"pid":"9b0df3ef9566459193312c91885f071afa8d9dac","tid":2506421,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T09:58:21.000Z","msg":"又有新籍口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df37670b70f83abe5cbe7ffacec19f0a4fcc98e","tid":2506421,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T09:58:43.000Z","msg":"睇黎你老母一定冇 畀你每日飲精一杯"},{"pid":"870d5f78219c4eba8dc382199184340ea4e118c9","tid":2506421,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:03:46.000Z","msg":"精液雖是體內代謝物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d1b4d441b1ed36438b47f1f1fc0d996270a4eee","tid":2506421,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:08:22.000Z","msg":"食自己果d有冇幫助？"},{"pid":"6fb7b57cc3711d2618a6de1de854090ffed84cef","tid":2506421,"uid":65984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:09:47.000Z","msg":"我最近都發覺自己蠢蠢地,有冇巴打可以幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52cf5f285d871fc7f2055f56616699d04a2d9b07","tid":2506421,"uid":160964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:11:14.000Z","msg":"儲左廿幾年終於有用了"},{"pid":"c99ec25025123a43ac1bdc7f0129a00492a6e5f5","tid":2506421,"uid":94454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:17:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />no homo"},{"pid":"e1968e723981505591b2e110ab27705af1ce3fdf","tid":2506421,"uid":246419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:19:59.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61650f2882f44c441b323d5aba83e0c2450dead6","tid":2506421,"uid":246419,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d1b4d441b1ed36438b47f1f1fc0d996270a4eee","tid":2506421,"uid":289946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:08:22.000Z","msg":"食自己果d有冇幫助？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:20:30.000Z","msg":"搵巴打啦 快d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b63516e9c421b81af13734c10cdd7eea424f23","tid":2506421,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:21:57.000Z","msg":"點解啲科學家會諗到做呢啲實驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b0110855f7ff0f544441e7ab9ff5070872e36b","tid":2506421,"uid":288071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0